name: Pump It Up: Exceed Portable
overview: he popular Korean rhythm action game Pump It Up EXCEED Portable is finally available on PSP. Everyone can playing "Pump It Up Exceed Portable!" at their home, work, and school. This game has great a assortment of 94 songs. There are K-Pop, Banya, and Pop tracks. Also, the 'Survival Mode' will be make you more exciting. Whenever you end a song or clear, you can appreciation of great image and music in the 'Music Video' part. Pump It Up Exceed Portable is faster than your eyes and your thinking.
